WEBVTT

00:07.875 --> 00:09.430
Previously on "Homeland"...

00:09.433 --> 00:11.285
I'm shredding documents and I see it...

00:11.288 --> 00:13.137
A gold pack of Nafisi's cigarettes.

00:13.139 --> 00:15.773
Mossad must have been briefing
him in that room before I arrived.

00:15.775 --> 00:17.442
You think the whole thing was a charade?

00:17.444 --> 00:20.144
- Awaiting confirmation.
- What kind of confirmation?

00:20.146 --> 00:21.645
Javadi.

00:21.647 --> 00:24.148
You want me to babysit?

00:24.150 --> 00:25.649
Would you?

00:27.520 --> 00:28.685
Terrorist!

00:32.491 --> 00:34.357
I want my mommy. I want my mommy!

00:34.359 --> 00:35.422
It's not safe.

00:35.425 --> 00:37.327
Got to get downstairs and out of sight.

00:37.329 --> 00:38.798
The shooter's position is confirmed.

00:38.800 --> 00:41.364
- Let's do it.
- No! You cannot do this!

00:41.366 --> 00:43.900
Did you hear me?! My
daughter is in there!

00:43.902 --> 00:45.434
- Move in!
- No!

00:45.436 --> 00:46.602
He's down!

00:46.604 --> 00:48.904
You said...

00:48.906 --> 00:50.372
"P-Protect Franny."

00:50.374 --> 00:51.740
Yes.

00:51.742 --> 00:52.908
Then you took me down.

00:52.910 --> 00:54.610
When my back was turned.

00:54.612 --> 00:55.755
What's this?

00:55.758 --> 00:57.613
Taken four hours before the explosion.

00:57.615 --> 00:59.215
You recognize the van?

00:59.217 --> 01:00.549
Who's that?

01:00.551 --> 01:02.783
I tracked down that blue Jeep,

01:02.785 --> 01:06.053
which then disappeared while I
was inside a very strange place.

01:06.055 --> 01:07.211
Strange how?

01:07.214 --> 01:09.491
I'm thinking we should
discuss in person.

01:09.493 --> 01:10.858
Can you get out to my house?

01:10.860 --> 01:11.993
Sure.

